WEBVTT

00:01:06.000 --> 00:01:09.000
Leave the Sewing to Claireping

00:01:17.000 --> 00:01:20.000
Romi! Are you still drawing?

00:01:21.000 --> 00:01:23.000
Yeah, I'm all done now. Here, look!

00:01:24.000 --> 00:01:28.000
Wow! Did you draw a monster, Claireping?

00:01:29.000 --> 00:01:31.000
Huh? How does this look like a monster?

00:01:32.000 --> 00:01:34.000
Look closely. This is a dress.

00:01:35.000 --> 00:01:38.000
Hey, there's no way something like this is a dress!

00:01:39.000 --> 00:01:42.000
It is a dress. It was my favorite dress when I was little.

00:01:43.000 --> 00:01:46.000
It was the first dress I ever wore.

00:01:47.000 --> 00:01:50.000
It's hard to call that a dress for a true princess.

00:01:52.000 --> 00:01:56.000
Hehe, okay! I will make you a real dress!

00:01:57.000 --> 00:02:00.000
Phew, it's fine, it's fine. I have homework... ugh.

00:02:03.000 --> 00:02:04.000
Hiya!

00:02:17.000 --> 00:02:19.000
It's already beautiful.

00:02:20.000 --> 00:02:21.000
I'm the best, as expected!

00:02:22.000 --> 00:02:25.000
Romi will really love this dress too, right?

00:02:43.000 --> 00:02:46.000
Romi! You're finally awake.

00:02:48.000 --> 00:02:52.000
You startled me, Claireping! Why are you... since morning...

00:02:53.000 --> 00:02:58.000
The masterpiece I made for you is finished! Now, come here! Come here!

00:03:00.000 --> 00:03:04.000
Ta-da! How is it? It's incredibly beautiful, right?

00:03:06.000 --> 00:03:07.000
Wh-what is?

00:03:08.000 --> 00:03:12.000
Oh please, you're joking. I'm talking about this beautiful dress here!

00:03:14.000 --> 00:03:17.000
It's perfect for when you shrink down, right?

00:03:18.000 --> 00:03:20.000
It's the latest Teenieping style in the kingdom.

00:03:21.000 --> 00:03:25.000
I don't need it. And my dress was in style back then too.

00:03:34.000 --> 00:03:36.000
She doesn't need the dress I made?

00:03:37.000 --> 00:03:40.000
I'm Claireping, Princess of the Fashion Kingdom.

00:03:43.000 --> 00:03:44.000
Wait a minute.

00:03:45.000 --> 00:03:47.000
Princess Sara's magazine has a lot to look at.

00:03:48.000 --> 00:03:51.000
Maybe the trends among humans are different from ours.

00:03:56.000 --> 00:03:58.000
What's with this needle?

00:03:59.000 --> 00:04:02.000
Who stuck a needle here? It's dangerous.

00:04:16.000 --> 00:04:19.000
Yeah, staying like this seems dangerous. I'll...

00:04:20.000 --> 00:04:24.000
No, I mean we should go check if Princess Romi is okay!

00:04:25.000 --> 00:04:29.000
Wait, you're just trying to drink water by yourself, aren't you?

00:04:31.000 --> 00:04:33.000
What? No, I'm not!

00:04:34.000 --> 00:04:37.000
What's this? Who brought this here?

00:04:38.000 --> 00:04:41.000
If Sara sees this, I'm the only one who'll get scolded.

00:04:59.000 --> 00:05:01.000
It's delicious!

00:05:03.000 --> 00:05:04.000
Claireping! What's wrong?

00:05:05.000 --> 00:05:07.000
What's the matter?

00:05:09.000 --> 00:05:10.000
Romi...

00:05:16.000 --> 00:05:18.000
Romi isn't coming out?

00:05:20.000 --> 00:05:22.000
My magic isn't working...

00:05:24.000 --> 00:05:28.000
Stop crying and calmly tell us what happened.

00:05:30.000 --> 00:05:34.000
Since earlier, my dress-making magic hasn't been working...

00:05:36.000 --> 00:05:41.000
When I do this, clothes are supposed to be made the way I want... but it's not working at all.

00:05:43.000 --> 00:05:46.000
Oh no! This is terrible! We're in big trouble!

00:05:50.000 --> 00:05:52.000
Princess Romi... Princess Romi...

00:05:53.000 --> 00:05:54.000
Why are you making a fuss again?

00:05:55.000 --> 00:05:57.000
She turned into a mannequin!

00:06:05.000 --> 00:06:08.000
This mannequin's appearance, it's definitely Romi.

00:06:10.000 --> 00:06:13.000
Romi! How did you turn into this!

00:06:18.000 --> 00:06:20.000
Guys, look over here!

00:06:21.000 --> 00:06:24.000
It says the first person to open this page will turn into a mannequin.

00:06:25.000 --> 00:06:28.000
Before midnight passes, using the included magic needle and infinite thread,

00:06:29.000 --> 00:06:33.000
you have to make clothes that satisfy the mannequin to break the magic.

00:06:35.000 --> 00:06:37.000
We have six hours left.

00:06:38.000 --> 00:06:40.000
However, it must be the one who received the mark of the needle.

00:06:41.000 --> 00:06:45.000
The needle might have fun magic hidden inside? Just kidding.

00:06:46.000 --> 00:06:48.000
What? This is a huge deal!

00:06:49.000 --> 00:06:54.000
First, the needle, where is the needle? There's nothing like a needle here!

00:06:56.000 --> 00:07:00.000
We will save Princess Romi! Let's search right now, let's go!

00:07:08.000 --> 00:07:10.000
We need to find the needle quickly!

00:07:11.000 --> 00:07:16.000
A needle... speaking of a needle... I got pricked by one earlier.

00:07:18.000 --> 00:07:20.000
Ah! Is this it?

00:07:22.000 --> 00:07:26.000
What is this? Uh, let me see.

00:07:27.000 --> 00:07:28.000
Huh? The thread is gone.

00:07:29.000 --> 00:07:30.000
Even when I try to grab it, it slips away.

00:07:31.000 --> 00:07:35.000
It seems Claireping is the one who received the mark of the needle.

00:07:41.000 --> 00:07:45.000
But I can't even use my dress-making magic right now, what do I do?

00:07:46.000 --> 00:07:48.000
You can just sew by hand!

00:07:49.000 --> 00:07:53.000
I've never sewn by hand before...

00:07:54.000 --> 00:07:56.000
Then have you only been making clothes with magic all this time?

00:07:57.000 --> 00:07:59.000
Of course. I'm a princess.

00:08:00.000 --> 00:08:04.000
There's no way I would do hand sewing.

00:08:06.000 --> 00:08:08.000
You can just learn this time!

00:08:10.000 --> 00:08:14.000
Here, like this, if you do this, one stitch is completed.

00:08:16.000 --> 00:08:17.000
Like this? Ouch, ow.

00:08:18.000 --> 00:08:19.000
Can you do it?

00:08:20.000 --> 00:08:22.000
I am Claireping, Princess of the Fashion Kingdom.

00:08:23.000 --> 00:08:26.000
I'll put my honor on the line and get it done!

00:08:28.000 --> 00:08:31.000
Marylou, the fashion magazine you sent had another weird magic spell on it.

00:08:31.000 --> 00:08:32.000
Did you open it?

00:08:33.000 --> 00:08:37.000
Yeah. This time I put a magic spell with a fashion designer and mannequin concept.

00:08:39.000 --> 00:08:43.000
But the curse on the needle only prevents them from making clothes with magic.

00:08:44.000 --> 00:08:47.000
Sigh, even if you are an Earth witch, you're going to get in big trouble doing that.

00:08:48.000 --> 00:08:52.000
It's fine. Once 12 o'clock passes... well, it'll work out somehow.

00:09:00.000 --> 00:09:03.000
I think I get the hang of hand sewing now!

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:18.000
I wonder what kind of dress Romi wants?

00:09:20.000 --> 00:09:22.000
Let's try a different design.

00:09:28.000 --> 00:09:29.000
Ah, ouch!

00:09:32.000 --> 00:09:35.000
I'll make you the most beautiful dress.

00:09:41.000 --> 00:09:42.000
Done.

00:09:42.000 --> 00:09:44.000
Please work this time!

00:09:50.000 --> 00:09:51.000
Romi.

00:09:51.000 --> 00:09:54.000
Don't tell me it's a failure again?

00:09:55.000 --> 00:09:59.000
If midnight passes like this, Romi, Romi will!

00:10:00.000 --> 00:10:04.000
Calm down, Claireping. We will definitely be able to turn Romi back.

00:10:05.000 --> 00:10:09.000
Yeah. We still have one hour left. You can make one more.

00:10:11.000 --> 00:10:14.000
But what kind of dress does Romi want...

00:10:25.000 --> 00:10:30.000
This is the drawing Romi made this morning... why is it glowing?

00:10:35.000 --> 00:10:40.000
Could the Magic Mirror have given us a hint?

00:10:41.000 --> 00:10:44.000
Then, for the last time, I'll try making this drawing into a dress.

00:10:45.000 --> 00:10:47.000
Yeah! Let's hurry!

00:11:06.000 --> 00:11:10.000
Claireping, there's no time! You have to finish it quickly!

00:11:11.000 --> 00:11:15.000
Please... please, please! One last stitch!

00:11:26.000 --> 00:11:28.000
Romi!

00:11:30.000 --> 00:11:34.000
I'm sorry... it's because I wasn't good enough...

00:11:46.000 --> 00:11:47.000
This dress is...

00:11:48.000 --> 00:11:50.000
Romi! You're back!

00:11:55.000 --> 00:11:59.000
More than any dress I've ever made, that dress suits you the best.

00:12:00.000 --> 00:12:02.000
This dress, did you guys make it?

00:12:03.000 --> 00:12:07.000
I only realized later what kind of dress you really like.

00:12:08.000 --> 00:12:11.000
I made it based on the drawing you drew.

00:12:12.000 --> 00:12:15.000
I really love it. Thank you, guys!

00:12:17.000 --> 00:12:18.000
Where is the needle!

00:12:19.000 --> 00:12:21.000
Answer me right now!

00:12:24.000 --> 00:12:28.000
It feels like looking for a needle in a sandy beach.

00:12:35.000 --> 00:12:38.000
Let me go when I tell you to stop. It hurts.

00:12:39.000 --> 00:12:40.000
Romi!